Business Brief -- Fluor Corp.:
   Unit's Jobs With the TVA
   Are Valued at $240 Million
The unit, FD Engineers  Constructors Inc., will perform
maintenance, modification and capital improvement services at
the plants. Fluor, based in Irvine, Calif., is an
engineering, construction, maintenance and technical services
company with investments in coal and lead.
   The TVA, based in Knoxville, Tenn., supplies electricity
to more than seven million people in Tennessee and parts of
Alabama, Georgia, Kentucky, Mississippi, North Carolina and
Virginia, Fluor said.